, journeyman silk-weaver, Great George-street, Bethnal-green;
Mary Robins
, 3, George-street; and
George Arrowsmith
, journeyman silk weaver, Edward-street, Bethnal-green, gave the prisoner a good character.

Robert Thompson
, house-painter and decorator;
